short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Visualize your chrome activity to determine your surfing habits.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension accesses your local browsing history to present to https://time-sink.vercel.app/ which consumes the data and provides a visual representation to allow users to get better insights to their habits.
(No personal data is ever shared to our servers)
